column5: Can anyone tell me about a trip with these people. Lakes cabin or anything.

Very nice people and will definately put you where there is fish and wildlife to be immensely enjoyed. I go to get my fishing license for Canada from these people every year. Hope you choose their outfit. best of luck!!!!
If you are in the Mpls/St.paul area, Larry is the the NW Sport Show this week. Also a good thing to talk face to face with the operator.BH
